---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="About" description="About UI Gems and its author">
  <div class="prose about">
    <h1>About UI Gems</h1>
    <p>
      UI Gems is a weekly technical writing series exploring advanced CSS
      techniques, experimental specifications, and the future of the web
      platform. Every article originates here and is cross-posted to Medium
      and LinkedIn. The interactive demos are exclusive to this site.
    </p>

    <h2>About the Author</h2>
    <p>
      Senior Frontend Engineer with deep expertise in CSS architecture, design
      systems, and modern web standards. Previously Staff Engineer at LinkedIn,
      where I built token-based design systems, a layout engine inspired by
      Flexbox and Compose, and Figma-to-code tooling that improved delivery
      speed by 40%.
    </p>

    <h2>Follow Along</h2>
    <p>
      Find me on <a href="https://medium.com/@projectluis">Medium</a>,
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/theluistorres">LinkedIn</a>, and
      <a href="https://github.com/semanticpixel">GitHub</a>. Or subscribe
      via <a href="/ui-gems/rss.xml">RSS</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: var(--content-width);
  }
</style>
